WEBVTT

00:07:59.875 --> 00:08:01.417
(Laughter)

00:08:03.167 --> 00:08:07.434
So in order to help you
understand this breakthrough,

00:08:07.458 --> 00:08:10.625
let me take you back 20 years to 1999.

00:08:12.208 --> 00:08:14.768
I was a graduate student
in Berkeley, California,

00:08:14.792 --> 00:08:16.893
studying the biophysics of HIV.

00:08:16.917 --> 00:08:19.101
For such a complex epidemic,

00:08:19.125 --> 00:08:22.708
the simplicity
of this virus fascinated me.

00:08:23.958 --> 00:08:27.893
HIV, like all viruses,
is just an instruction set --

00:08:27.917 --> 00:08:29.226
malware.

00:08:29.250 --> 00:08:34.143
It hijacks a cell and converts
that cell into a factory to do one thing: